Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.60,0:00:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家 卡萊多之星要開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀看卡萊多之星時請注意保持室內明亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.10,0:00:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.50,0:00:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那麼 那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.80,0:00:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家有沒有將自己的心情告訴喜歡的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.70,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.40,0:00:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～真羞人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.90,0:00:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢 波力士已經決定向凱特求婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.20,0:00:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波力士的臉雖然有點可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.70,0:00:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可為人非常溫柔害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.50,0:00:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿出點勇氣來 沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.70,0:00:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對嗎？健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你怎麼沒精打采的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說要你做我的搭檔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.10,0:02:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.60,0:02:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.60,0:02:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.80,0:02:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠……能夠成為我的搭檔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.10,0:02:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這樣 萊恩先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲 索菲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.50,0:02:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.40,0:02:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.70,0:02:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊恩先生還有另外一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平時那個冷酷的萊恩不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫暖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.50,0:03:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過和萊恩先生爭鬥的事……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.40,0:03:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定不在舞臺上和他爭鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能成為他的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.40,0:03:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走的路和萊恩先生的、和蕾拉小姐的都不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.60,0:03:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.20,0:03:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從我回到舞臺的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.50,0:03:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所要的舞臺是令觀眾和表演者都充滿笑容\N沒有爭鬥的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.80,0:03:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想創建的是那樣的卡萊多的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好緊張啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.10,0:03:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呢 早就猜到你會這個樣子 送你個禮物好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬納森 準備好的東西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.40,0:04:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全約會手冊 奪得她芳心的100種方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 如果你不想輸給萊恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.90,0:04:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得在這方面下功夫奪得她的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪得她的心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.10,0:04:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心啦 這身打扮很適合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.20,0:04:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不能讓人高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且打扮成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.60,0:04:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一想到會被她逼著合作的時……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是一種樂趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她虛弱的時候就是機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.10,0:04:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔的安慰她時 就可以約她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上一頓美味的午飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.50,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣她的心就不設防
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.40,0:04:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以如你所願啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我可不對健抱什麼期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.70,0:04:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓空振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.60,0:04:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但……但是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健 多謝你長久來的關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.50,0:04:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和健不是戀人關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.70,0:04:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 疼嗎？健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.70,0:04:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 你怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有撞到頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她虛弱的時候就是機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 現在不是想這個的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.30,0:05:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍一不留神就撞到你了 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不留神？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來探病？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又好像不像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.50,0:05:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想可以的話一起吃午飯怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.10,0:05:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.90,0:05:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說健為了鼓勵我才穿成這樣來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.80,0:05:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一說我最近老是讓大家擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.00,0:05:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 既然這樣得讓健高興高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.60,0:05:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 我正好餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.80,0:05:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.60,0:05:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.30,0:05:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身衣服挺配你的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.20,0:05:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.50,0:06:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 決定和阿娜合作了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去換身衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.10,0:06:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難說……呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家店的菜超好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.60,0:06:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有是在那邊的平臺屋頂座席風景超棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.50,0:06:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周我也剛和中學的朋友一起來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.60,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了 就在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.00,0:06:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒閉了的冰激淩店？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.10,0:06:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.70,0:06:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.70,0:06:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊……還有這街道過去有家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.30,0:06:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這條街有家保鈴球館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼偏偏這個時候……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.50,0:06:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那本書的地圖有錯誤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.80,0:07:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為爸爸就是靠那本書得到媽媽的芳心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多少年前了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.90,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生前的事 不要問我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.60,0:07:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健好像有所行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是照著手冊上說的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.00,0:07:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在美好的時代裏是需要明確的判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去的店倒閉了的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.10,0:07:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要猶豫 盡力回想記憶中這附近其他的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.50,0:07:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往就是需要愛的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.40,0:07:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到健也會發呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.20,0:07:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有賣熱狗的店哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就吃熱狗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健 雖然沒有陽臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以看到海哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.80,0:07:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色又好天氣又好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠閒的過日子真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.60,0:08:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你邀請我 健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.30,0:08:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可以被動呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果不儘快掌握主導權的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.20,0:08:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣真的是好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 心情真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好天氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出點勇氣來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.20,0:08:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是波力士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波力士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.60,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空……空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波力士 拜託你別跑那麼快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.80,0:08:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 拜託你了 幫幫我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波……波力士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向凱特求婚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.70,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 小時候就夢想在30歲的時候給她一個浪漫的求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.60,0:09:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不是怕被拒絕所以說不出口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.10,0:09:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因為和我很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.00,0:09:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你30歲的生日是哪天呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.00,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得快點去找凱特啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是今天醫院也休息 哪里都找不到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.80,0:09:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我休息居然見不到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.30,0:09:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來夢想還是讓它成為美夢更好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波力士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.60,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想還是讓它成為美夢更好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 夢想是為了實現而存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是為了這個什麼都可以付出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波力士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波力士 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.60,0:09:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去實現夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.50,0:09:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣氛變得很微妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正空振作就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要先找到凱特才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能找到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.20,0:10:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰的不巧可不好辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不能老是朝著後面看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會一定會來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要這麼相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.50,0:10:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空說的有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.00,0:10:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以這麼垂頭喪氣的 健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有機會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個不就是凱特嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 凱特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅貝魯特 等很久了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.70,0:10:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我沒有什麼勝算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那種事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.00,0:10:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來男人不是只有外表啊才能啊錢啊之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要有熱情和真心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.90,0:10:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱特小姐很清楚你的長處的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我先去確認一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 空 確認？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.30,0:10:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.60,0:10:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現不了的夢想還是放棄比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.50,0:11:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我要說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種訓練我得練到什麼時候啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個感覺不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這種感覺自然的笑出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得在和萊恩、空同台演出時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀眾們看到的你是什麼樣的表情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.30,0:11:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.60,0:11:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如我所料還真是花時間呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.60,0:11:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也算特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人是在演出嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電臺在攝影？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.30,0:11:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是普通的怪人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是別搭理他們比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.70,0:11:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像越來越麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.10,0:11:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不被拆穿真面目 得好好隱藏才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.60,0:11:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拆穿了就沒臉去學校了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 羅貝魯特只是我的同事而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.50,0:11:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天只是陪我買東西的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.20,0:11:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.70,0:11:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼問這個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.90,0:11:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是隨口問問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剛才飯才吃了一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.60,0:12:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼去吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.90,0:12:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我發薪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.00,0:12:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先陪我去銀行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.50,0:12:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得先告訴波力士讓他安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不明白她在表達些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是很不安啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在這個時候……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不好的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.30,0:12:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是有人打劫銀行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的把錢交出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.30,0:13:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是世界第一黴運男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.80,0:13:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.60,0:13:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.40,0:13:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波力士(員警) 健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,員警？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把凱特放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.10,0:13:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 有生第一次打劫銀行居然有員警混進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然是世界第一黴運男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.00,0:13:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們應該知道我說的是真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2樓的那個傢伙你給我下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你把那個員警綁起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.30,0:13:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁緊點 待會我要檢查的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.50,0:13:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繩子不夠的話我的包裏還有很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.30,0:13:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶總是表揚我準備工作做得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了 波力士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.00,0:13:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聽他的話你就危險了 綁緊一點好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.70,0:13:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 警車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:14:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我靠 把員警叫來的話 就不是只要錢就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想這麼說 可我做得到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.90,0:14:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一舉一動已經被銀行的監視器記錄得一清二楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.10,0:14:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.10,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真是世界第一倒楣的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.90,0:14:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像真的是有人打劫銀行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.10,0:14:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.40,0:14:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強盜聽著 乖乖的放了人質 老實的出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.90,0:14:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那裏的情況我們這裏全部能清楚的看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面的人都沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.50,0:14:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在投降的話還不算嚴重哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.80,0:14:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 看得見嗎 到底怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.40,0:14:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你在這一天做了多惡劣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.40,0:14:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空和健都沒事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.60,0:14:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 外邊全是些自以為是的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.90,0:14:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也沒那麼壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.40,0:14:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣的想法直到現在……都沒實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.90,0:15:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想需要錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒多少也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.10,0:15:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想很小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在守衛休息的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在銀行的人不在的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.70,0:15:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不打算要用女人當人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.10,0:15:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後得到我小小的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.80,0:15:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那麼一點點夢想都實現不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.30,0:15:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我嗎？我的責任嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的夢想呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.10,0:15:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.20,0:15:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.90,0:15:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會實現 我一定會實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.80,0:15:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真夠堅定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.60,0:15:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要創造 讓所有人能露出笑容的卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是卡萊多劇團的演員？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.70,0:15:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不過是弄虛作假罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄虛作假是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.50,0:15:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇表演絕對不是弄虛作假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是卡萊多劇團的演員阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不相信那套了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.00,0:15:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人身註定不是隨便相信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是親眼看見的絕對不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.60,0:16:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是有如此覺悟的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓你看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.20,0:16:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.20,0:16:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就在這裏表演給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就在這裏……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 現在不是做這個的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.40,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.30,0:16:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在 在和這位小姐談論夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.30,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相干的人別插嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.80,0:16:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過 要讓所有的觀眾露出笑容的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.90,0:16:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.60,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓我露出笑容吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓擁有鐵石心腸的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.20,0:16:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 喂 好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繩子借我用用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.80,0:16:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請盡情觀賞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.30,0:16:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到能看到女孩表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 空她……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在表演？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.80,0:17:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看想看想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空在哪個銀行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.90,0:17:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不去就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在笑嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.10,0:17:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這裏 我就在想會不會在之前來過的這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.80,0:17:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要點呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.80,0:17:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從美亞來的聯絡 說空現在銀行在員警們都在看的電視前現場表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一起看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事態不允許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了不就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.30,0:17:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.60,0:17:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 我還會繼續努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.80,0:17:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅也去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 連我也一起載了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是為了讓你們載我才說那些話的 是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.40,0:18:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過熱鬧點才有趣嘛 雖然擠了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.70,0:18:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這裏就是我的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.10,0:18:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了在看著我的觀眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.30,0:18:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要全力表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.40,0:18:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.80,0:18:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.10,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的騰空了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.70,0:18:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家讓我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.10,0:18:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀眾的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.10,0:18:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精彩的演技 在舞臺上演繹的人們都十分的高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.40,0:18:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我喜歡卡萊多劇團的原因之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.50,0:18:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道媽媽和爸爸已經不會再回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.70,0:18:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,察覺到的時候 就和平時卡萊多劇團裏所想的很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.90,0:19:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得如果繼續留在卡萊多劇團的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.50,0:19:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能找回那時候的快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.80,0:19:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.40,0:19:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是空贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.70,0:19:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道為什麼空這麼賣力嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.60,0:19:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是為了證明卡萊多不是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.10,0:19:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空希望你能找回微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不單單只你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.60,0:19:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的目標是讓看到自己表演的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.20,0:19:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起在舞臺上表演的人們 都獲得微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.50,0:19:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想製造讓客人和觀眾們都開心的卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.40,0:19:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那的確是困難的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空深信自己能夠實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.80,0:19:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.00,0:20:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想為了我的夢想稍稍努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.50,0:20:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.80,0:20:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要向她求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.70,0:20:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不輸給你的夢想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的不算是夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.50,0:20:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想把敗狗找回來而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再嘗試一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.60,0:20:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是也這麼打算的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.00,0:20:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.80,0:20:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.00,0:20:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住我的不是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.90,0:20:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 夠了 我已經知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.20,0:20:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收回說你騙人的話 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.60,0:20:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.60,0:20:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次請來卡萊多劇團看表演吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾 結束了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.70,0:20:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來還真棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.00,0:20:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊 空 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.80,0:21:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空還是那麼厲害呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很不甘心 不過的確是很棒的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.40,0:21:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是在舞臺 到底是什麼 我心中對空的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.70,0:21:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.40,0:21:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又回到了童年時光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.00,0:21:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被欺負的愛哭鬼傑瑞 還真來救我了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.40,0:21:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不願意 可是身體還是不由自主地……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.50,0:21:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔就傑瑞好的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.80,0:21:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.30,0:21:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想抓你一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.40,0:21:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你30歲生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.40,0:21:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想抓住你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.80,0:22:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓空在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.00,0:22:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也只有舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.90,0:22:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射手座的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.10,0:22:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造出笑容的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.20,0:22:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是很不現實的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.40,0:22:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都有不現實的路要走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.50,0:22:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經走在前面的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.40,0:22:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是會喝彩？還是會嘲笑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.90,0:22:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會是這其中之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.70,0:23:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告\N卡萊多之星 新生之翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.10,0:23:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼 這個幼稚的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.80,0:23:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事 還是大家的笑容最棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.80,0:23:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空有而我卻沒有的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.80,0:23:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很不甘心 我一定要找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.30,0:23:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雅格尼斯先生的指導下 劇團最強的組合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.50,0:23:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 羅傑特 上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.40,0:24:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 空老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.30,0:24:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.00,0:24:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀是夢想 飛向空
